<p><span class="spip_note_ref">[<a href="#nh23" class="spip_note" title="Footnotes 23" rev="footnote">23</a>]&nbsp;</span><i>Le Combat syndicaliste</i>, 5 June 1936.</p>
</div><div id="nb24">
